'''Mugruebe stew''' was a special [[Agamar/Legends|Agamarian]] meal that was made from the flesh of the [[mugruebe]], although its popularity throughout the rest of [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]] was limited. It was usually prepared with roots and tree bark. Not surprisingly, mugruebe stew was a favorite of [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]] [[Starfighter/Legends|starfighter]] [[Pilot/Legends|pilot]] [[Keyan Farlander/Legends|Keyan Farlander]], who was a native of that [[Planet/Legends|world]].

